            <title>Math 121 Week 9 Activity</title>

        <objectives>
		<p>
            In this activity we will do the following:
        </p>
        <ul>
	  		<li>
	  			<p>
					Derive the identities for the sine and cosine of sum and differences of angles.
	  			</p>
	  		</li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    Use these identities to find exact expressions for sines and cosines of more angles than the "special" angles.
                </p>
            </li>
	  	</ul>
    </objectives>
            <introduction>
                <p>
